# ── Velopack release artefacts (regenerated by build-release.ps1 / CI) ──────
# These are large binary outputs (Setup.exe, *.nupkg, RELEASES) that should
# be uploaded to GitHub Releases, not committed to the repo. Local copies are
# kept under releases/ for delta package generation against the previous build.
releases/

# ── Runtime artefacts (generated beside EXE) ─────────────────────────────────
*.settings.json
*.log
*.log.bak
*.log.tmp
build.log

# ── Strong-name keys (kept out of repo; CI injects from secrets) ─────────────
# NOTE: NepDateWidget.snk is currently committed for build convenience. If you
# rotate the key, do NOT commit the new one — store it in CI secrets instead.
#*.snk

